cu.explanation_en: Setting the local S port D to 0 is out of range for valid port numbers and will cause socket binding failure, preventing F1 interface communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the local N port D to 0 is out of range for valid port numbers and will cause binding failure for F1 interface.
du.explanation_zh: 將本地 N 端口 D 設定為 0 超出有效端口號範圍，會導致 F1 介面的綁定失敗。
